// ============================================================
// inject_rtti_err_set_non_string.lox — Non-string set element error
// ============================================================
// Setup: cust = TCustomer with Flags property (TCustomerFlags set).
//
// What this tests:
//   - Writing a set array with a non-string element produces a runtime error

print cust.Name; // expect: Alice
cust.Flags = ["cfVIP", 42]; // expect runtime error: Set elements must be strings (enum names).
